===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|s}}

# {{lb|en|uncountable|finance}} The price paid for obtaining, or price received for providing, [[money]] or [[goods]] in a [[credit]] [[transaction]], calculated as a fraction of the amount or value of what was [[borrow]]ed. {{defdate|from earlier 16th c.}}
#: {{ux|en|Our bank offers borrowers an annual '''interest''' of 5%.}}
# {{lb|en|uncountable}} A great [[attention]] and concern from someone or something; intellectual [[curiosity]]. {{defdate|from later 18th c.}}
#: {{ux|en|He has a lot of '''interest''' in vintage cars.}}
