# {{lb|en|countable}} Something or someone one is interested in.
#: {{ux|en|Lexicography is one of my '''interests'''.}}
#: {{ux|en|Victorian furniture is an '''interest''' of mine.}}
#: {{ux|en|The main character's romantic '''interest''' will be played by a non-professional actor.}}
# {{lb|en|obsolete|rare}} [[injury|Injury]], or compensation for injury; [[damage]]s.
#* {{RQ:Florio Montaigne Essayes|chapter=12|book=II|passage=How can this infinite beauty, power and goodnes admit any correspondencie or similitude with a thing so base and abject as we are, without extreme '''interest''' and manifest derogation from his divine greatnesse?}}
